column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, x.objID,   s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.z,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, s.special_target1, s.sourceType, g.lgm_tot_p5# FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID  JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra as g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
